  "prompt": "Where can someone find a free good virtual piano keyboard that displays the music sheets upon the keyboard?",
  "response": "There are several websites and software options that offer free virtual piano keyboards with the ability to display music sheets directly on the keys. Here are some popular ones:\n\n1. **OnlinePianist**\n   - **Website**: [OnlinePianist](https://www.onlinepianist.com/)\n   - **Features**: Offers a virtual piano with a variety of songs to practice. It displays the notes on the keyboard as you play along with the sheet music.\n\n2. **Virtual Piano**\n   - **Website**: [Virtual Piano](https://virtualpiano.net/)\n   - **Features**: A simple and straightforward virtual piano that allows you to play using your computer keyboard. It also includes a library of songs and shows the notes on the keyboard.\n\n3. **Pianu**\n   - **Website**: [Pianu](https://pianu.com/)\n   - **Features**: An interactive online piano that teaches you how to play by showing the notes on the keyboard. It includes lessons, sheet music, and the ability to see which keys to press.\n\n4. **OneMotion**\n   - **Website**: [OneMotion Virtual Piano](http://www.onemotion.com/flash/virtual-piano/)\n   - **Features**: A flash-based virtual piano that displays the notes on the keyboard as you play. It also allows you to record and play along with your recordings.\n\n5. **Synthesia**\n   - **Website**: [Synthesia](https://www.synthesiagame.com/)\n   - **Features**: A downloadable software that turns your computer into a virtual piano. It includes a \"falling notes\" display that shows you which keys to press, similar to a keyboard music sheet.\n\n6. **Musescore**\n   - **Website**: [Musescore](https://musescore.org/)\n   - **Features**: A comprehensive music notation software that includes a virtual piano. You can view and play along with sheet music directly within the application. The virtual piano feature is available in the recent versions.\n\nEach of these options offers a unique set of features, so you might want to try a few to see which one best suits your needs.",
